movie_title: Star Wars: Episode I - The Phantom Menace
title: It lived up to it's hype
review: I saw Episode I twice on opening night at 12:01am and 7:00pm.  My initial reaction was 'that was it?'  Maybe it was too late, but all day I was dying to see it again.  The second time was even better and I can't wait to see Episodes II and III
